CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 3, 1954, pg. 26 reads: 'Top Performers - Shown above are some of the standout stars in the annual Allegheny Mountain Association track and field meet held at Oliver Field last Saturday...In the right hand photo, left to right, are Leo Keys, Mount Union College; Bert Patterson, Mount Union College, and Sanford Smalley of Ammon. All were point winners for their respective teams.- Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Leo Keys, Bert Patterson, and Sanford Smalley, holding medals, posed on Oliver Field during annual Allegheny Mountain Association track and field championships, Oliver High School
